song_lyrics: Sufaḷ faḷī hu to Harine maḷī, āj Ekādashī sufaḷ faḷī... °ṭek
Chop karī naṭnāgar sāru, sej sajī kāju kusum kaḷī... āj° 1
Rasbas hoy rahī rasiyā sang, jyu misarī paymāhī bhaḷī... āj° 2
Nitya nitya prem rahu ur dharatī, Haricharaṇe man vṛutti haḷī... āj° 3
Brahmānand kahe Hari ur dhariyā, janma maraṇ kerī shankā ṭaḷī... āj° 4
title: Sufaḷ faḷī hu to Harine maḷī
